lead_paragraph: Sulman Raza made a 7-foot birdie putt on the third extra hole to outlast Taylor Funk and give Oregon its first NCAA men's golf title, 3-2 over short-handed Texas on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Raza Gives Oregon Its First NCAA Golf Title With Playoff Win
